Package org.opencart.exceptions

package org.opencart.exceptions
  • Exceptions
    Class
    Description
    BrowserInitializationFailedException
    Thrown when browser initialization fails due to some unknown reasons.
    FileOperationsFailedException
    Thrown when file operations fail due to unknown reasons.
    FrameworkExceptions
    FrameworkExceptions is a superclass for all the custom exceptions that can occur.
    InvalidBrowserException
    Thrown when browser value passed via excel file is not valid.
    InvalidExcelPathException
    Thrown when the excel file is not found due to invalid path mentioned in FrameworkConstants.
    InvalidPropertyFilePathException
    Thrown when the properties file is not found due to invalid path mentioned in FrameworkConstants.
    InvalidPropertyKeyException
    Thrown when property key mentioned in ConfigProperties is not valid.
    PropertyKeyNullException
    Thrown when null is passed where valid property key is required.
    PropertyValueEmptyException
    Thrown when value of property key mentioned in properties file is empty.
